**Summary:** This documentation covers Amplitude Experiment's Python SDK for server-side feature flag evaluation, supporting both remote evaluation (fetch_v2) and local evaluation (evaluate_v2) modes, with Python 3.6+ compatibility, cohort targeting via CohortSyncConfig, automatic assignment tracking, and AmplitudeCookie utilities for client-server device ID synchronization.

